# Level 99 Portfolio Project Detail Page Engineering Prompt

Based on comprehensive research across cutting-edge frontend technologies and design best practices, here's your complete engineering prompt for creating a stunning, production-ready portfolio project detail page for the LedgerIQ case study.

## Project Overview

**Objective**: Create a world-class portfolio project detail page showcasing the LedgerIQ case study using the most advanced frontend development techniques available in 2024-2025. The page should demonstrate expert-level skills in modern CSS, React patterns, animation systems, and responsive design while maintaining exceptional performance and accessibility.

## Core Technology Stack

### Essential Dependencies
```bash
# Install required packages
npm install @radix-ui/react-slot @radix-ui/react-dialog @radix-ui/react-tabs
npm install framer-motion tailwindcss
npm install lucide-react class-variance-authority clsx tailwind-merge
npm install @next/font next/image next/link

# Install Shadcn UI components
npx shadcn-ui@latest add button card badge separator aspect-ratio
npx shadcn-ui@latest add carousel tabs dialog sheet progress tooltip
npx shadcn-ui@latest add sidebar chart

# Install Motion Primitives
npx motion-primitives@latest add text-effect in-view
```

