            </h2>
            <p className="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              By reimagining the user experience and streamlining complex financial workflows, 
              LedgerIQ achieved significant improvements across all key performance indicators.
            </p>
          </div>
        </InView>
        
        <div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
